        in Lincoln? Think you might be a good fit for our team?
      </p>
      <p class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a
          href="/contact-us"
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex items-center uppercase py-3 px-16 rounded-md
                 hover:bg-blue-600 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium
                 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
                 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:ring-offset-white"
        >
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
